      "message": "Split BIP54 into bundle constituents\n\nAdd Draft BIPs for the timestamp-boundary fix, the legacy sigops transaction limit, and coinbase locktime duplicate prevention. Reuse existing BIP53 for the 64-byte transaction rule, update BIP54 to require all four constituent BIPs, and refresh the README table plus BIP54 test-vector descriptions.",
