      "updated_at": "2026-05-25T16:39:09Z",
      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "Concept ACK\r\n\r\nAs I wrote in https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/1800#pullrequestreview-2788772574, I'd prefer to see separate, focused BIPs, as recommended in both BIP 2 and BIP 3.\r\n\r\nBIP 2: *It is highly recommended that a single BIP contain a single key proposal or new idea. The more focused the BIP, the more successful it tends to be. If in doubt, split your BIP into several well-focused ones.*\r\n\r\nBIP 3: *It is recommended that complicated proposals be split into separate BIPs that each focus on a specific component of the overall proposal.*",
      "user": {
