      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "BIP 54 bundles together four items related in that they are minimal fixes for long term bugs in the consensus protocol. This is a complete document that describes a consistent set of changes that we (the authors) propose to the Bitcoin community. I understand that you favour a different mitigation for one of these bugs, but i would ask you to propose it to the Bitcoin community by authoring your own BIP rather than by modifying our own. Therefore NACK on this PR as it stands.",
