      "updated_at": "2026-05-26T20:04:49Z",
      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "As you point out, the modification you’re suggesting was already discussed before this proposal was published over a year ago. As you are aware, the authors explicitly declined to adopt this suggestion then. At this point it is clear that this suggestion does not match the BIP authors’ intended proposition.\r\n\r\n> Alternatively, I could put forth new BIPs (under my or other authoriship?) and later BIP-54 could later be pared down to REQUIRES these?\r\n\r\nIt is up to the authors of BIP54 to decide what they want to put forth to the community. Please submit your own proposal, instead of trying to take control of the scope of an existing proposal.",
